data.description: Let the light shine in this cozy 2 bedroom, 1 bath and extended 1 car garage beauty!  Enjoy the large deck, and enjoy the breeze flow. Great Room with soaring vaulted ceiling, and wall length sliding glass doors. The utility room is on the main floor.  Updated mechanicals: air conditioning unit installed 2016, 11 yr. old furnace and hot water heater 2020, Roof replaced in 7/28/2023, Gutters and siding 8/4/2023 and new flooring installed in living room in 2021.  If you need storage space, there is a large outdoor storage shed. Close to shopping, and a few minutes from the tollway.  The upcoming Casino that will soon open will be a boost to the neighborhood. Come see this totally charming ranch with an open floor plan, and expansive backyard with privacy deck that has a beautiful view.  The house is perfectly located within Naperville school district 204.  The house is being sold "As is."
